AGENTS.md
=========

AI Agent Engineering Guidelines
===============================

This repository supports AI-assisted development.

All AI coding agents (Codex, Claude, etc.) must follow the rules
defined in this document when implementing features or modifying code.

0. `apa簡要說明` Shortcut
--------------------------------------------------

If the user says any of these:

- `apa簡要說明`
- `apa 簡要說明`
- `apa說明`
- `apa 說明`

do not summarize this file.
Return only this short usage block:

- 開始實作循環：`apa prompt` -> 把輸出貼給 agent -> 明確要求使用 `apa-loop` + `apa-implement`
- 先交互修改文件：`apa prompt --docs-only` -> 把輸出貼給 agent -> 明確要求只使用 `apa-doc-review`
- Terminal loop wrapper：`bash scripts/apa-loop-setup.sh --max-iterations 30 --reviewer agent-self`
- 停止 wrapper：`bash scripts/apa-loop-cancel.sh`


